@media/@container atoms sort by breakpoint inside their bucket:
min-width ascending first (mobile-first: wider wins), then max-width
descending (desktop-first: narrower wins), then unparseable conditions in
first-occurrence order.

  $ cat > media.ml <<EOF
  > [@@@css "@media print {.css-p{display:none;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (max-width: 480px) {.css-d{color:red;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (max-width: 900px) {.css-c{color:green;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (min-width: 1200px) {.css-b{color:blue;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (min-width: 600px) {.css-a{color:black;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (orientation: landscape) {.css-q{color:gray;}}"]
  > EOF

  $ styled-ppx.generate media.ml
  /* This file is generated by styled-ppx, do not edit manually */
  @media (min-width: 600px) {.css-a{color:black;}}
  @media (min-width: 1200px) {.css-b{color:blue;}}
  @media (max-width: 900px) {.css-c{color:green;}}
  @media (max-width: 480px) {.css-d{color:red;}}
  @media print {.css-p{display:none;}}
  @media (orientation: landscape) {.css-q{color:gray;}}

Range syntax with `width` on the left participates in the same ordering;
em/rem convert at 16px for comparison purposes.

  $ cat > range.ml <<EOF
  > [@@@css "@container (width < 650px) {.css-d{font-size:1em;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@container (width > 800px) {.css-c{font-size:2em;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@container (width >= 20em) {.css-b{font-size:1.5em;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (width >= 200px) {.css-a{color:red;}}"]
  > EOF

  $ styled-ppx.generate range.ml
  /* This file is generated by styled-ppx, do not edit manually */
  @media (width >= 200px) {.css-a{color:red;}}
  @container (width >= 20em) {.css-b{font-size:1.5em;}}
  @container (width > 800px) {.css-c{font-size:2em;}}
  @container (width < 650px) {.css-d{font-size:1em;}}

Combined min+max conditions classify by their lower bound (mobile-first).

  $ cat > combined.ml <<EOF
  > [@@@css "@media (min-width: 900px) {.css-b{color:blue;}}"]
  > [@@@css "@media (min-width: 300px) and (max-width: 600px) {.css-a{color:red;}}"]
  > EOF

  $ styled-ppx.generate combined.ml
  /* This file is generated by styled-ppx, do not edit manually */
  @media (min-width: 300px) and (max-width: 600px) {.css-a{color:red;}}
  @media (min-width: 900px) {.css-b{color:blue;}}
